Here is a single self-contained HTML file that does exactly that:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>String Reverser</title>
  <style>
    /* ── Reset & Base ── */
    *, *::before, *::after {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0c29, #302b63, #24243e);
      color: #f0f0f0;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    /* ── Card ── */
    .card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 48px 40px;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 640px;
      box-shadow:
        0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.04) inset;
    }

    /* ── Header ── */
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    .header .icon {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0);   }
      50%       { transform: translateY(-8px); }
    }

    .header h1 {
      font-size: 1.9rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #a78bfa, #60a5fa, #34d399);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .header p {
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    }

    /* ── Input ── */
    .input-wrapper {
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .input-wrapper label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    #userInput {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
      border-radius: 14px;
      color: #f0f0f0;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s, background 0.25s;
      caret-color: #a78bfa;
    }

    #userInput::placeholder {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.22);
    }

    #userInput:focus {
      border-color: #a78bfa;
      background: rgba(167,139,250,0.08);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(167,139,250,0.15);
    }

    /* char counter */
    .char-count {
      position: absolute;
      right: 14px;
      bottom: -22px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .char-count.warn { color: #f59e0b; }
    .char-count.max  { color: #ef4444; }

    /* ── Divider ── */
    .divider {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      margin: 36px 0 24px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .divider::before,
    .divider::after {
      content: '';
      flex: 1;
      height: 1px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }

    /* ── Output Box ── */
    .output-label {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .output-box {
      min-height: 72px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      word-break: break-all;
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .output-box.has-content {
      border-color: rgba(96,165,250,0.35);
    }

    /* placeholder text inside output */
    .output-placeholder {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      user-select: none;
    }

    /* ── Animated Characters ── */
    .char-span {
      display: inline-block;
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(10px) scale(0.85);
      animation: charIn 0.22s ease forwards;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    @keyframes charIn {
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
      }
    }

    /* colour cycling for characters */
    .char-span:nth-child(5n+1) { color: #a78bfa; }
    .char-span:nth-child(5n+2) { color: #60a5fa; }
    .char-span:nth-child(5n+3) { color: #34d399; }
    .char-span:nth-child(5n+4) { color: #f9a8d4; }
    .char-span:nth-child(5n+5) { color: #fbbf24; }

    /* space characters */
    .char-span.space { color: transparent !important; }

    /* ── Stats Row ── */
    .stats {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .stat-pill {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 120px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.09);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .stat-pill .stat-value {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #a78bfa, #60a5fa);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .stat-pill .stat-label {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
      margin-top: 2px;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    /* ── Copy Button ── */
    .copy-btn {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 22px;
      padding: 14px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 14px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a78bfa, #60a5fa);
      color: #fff;
      transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(167,139,250,0.35);
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }

    .copy-btn:hover:not(:disabled) {
      opacity: 0.9;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(167,139,250,0.45);
    }

    .copy-btn:active:not(:disabled) {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    .copy-btn:disabled {
      opacity: 0.35;
      cursor: not-allowed;
      box-shadow: none;
    }

    .copy-btn.copied {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #34d399, #059669);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(52,211,153,0.35);
    }

    /* ── Clear Button ── */
    .clear-btn {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 6px;
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 10px;
      padding: 11px;
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border-radius: 14px;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      background: transparent;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }

    .clear-btn:hover:not(:disabled) {
      background: rgba(239,68,68,0.1);
      border-color: rgba(239,68,68,0.4);
      color: #fca5a5;
    }

    .clear-btn:disabled {
      opacity: 0.3;
      cursor: not-allowed;
    }

    /* ── Palindrome Badge ── */
    .palindrome-badge {
      display: none;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 6px;
      margin-top: 16px;
      padding: 9px 16px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(251,191,36,0.15), rgba(245,158,11,0.1));
      border: 1px solid rgba(251,191,36,0.3);
      color: #fbbf24;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.4px;
      animation: badgeIn 0.35s ease;
    }

    .palindrome-badge.show { display: flex; }

    @keyframes badgeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.85); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    }

    /* ── Responsive ── */
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .card { padding: 32px 22px; }
      .header h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="header">
    <span class="icon">🔄</span>
    <h1>String Reverser</h1>
    <p>Type below and watch your text flip in real time</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Input -->
  <div class="input-wrapper">
    <label for="userInput">Your Text</label>
    <input
      type="text"
      id="userInput"
      placeholder="Start typing here…"
      maxlength="200"
      autocomplete="off"
      spellcheck="false"
    />
    <span class="char-count" id="charCount">0 / 200</span>
  </div>

  <!-- Divider -->
  <div class="divider">REVERSED OUTPUT</div>

  <!-- Output -->
  <div class="output-label">Result</div>
  <div class="output-box" id="outputBox">
    <span class="output-placeholder" id="outputPlaceholder">Your reversed text will appear here…</span>
  </div>

  <!-- Palindrome Badge -->
  <div class="palindrome-badge" id="palindromeBadge">
    ⭐ Palindrome detected! It reads the same both ways.
  </div>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <div class="stats">
    <div class="stat-pill">
      <div class="stat-value" id="statChars">0</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Characters</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-pill">
      <div class="stat-value" id="statWords">0</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Words</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-pill">
      <div class="stat-value" id="statUnique">0</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Unique Chars</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Buttons -->
  <button class="copy-btn" id="copyBtn" disabled>
    <span id="copyIcon">📋</span>
    <span id="copyText">Copy Reversed Text</span>
  </button>
  <button class="clear-btn" id="clearBtn" disabled>
    ✕ Clear
  </button>

</div>

<script>
  // ── Element References ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  const userInput         = document.getElementById('userInput');
  const outputBox         = document.getElementById('outputBox');
  const outputPlaceholder = document.getElementById('outputPlaceholder');
  const charCountEl       = document.getElementById('charCount');
  const palindromeBadge   = document.getElementById('palindromeBadge');
  const statChars         = document.getElementById('statChars');
  const statWords         = document.getElementById('statWords');
  const statUnique        = document.getElementById('statUnique');
  const copyBtn           = document.getElementById('copyBtn');
  const copyIcon          = document.getElementById('copyIcon');
  const copyText          = document.getElementById('copyText');
  const clearBtn          = document.getElementById('clearBtn');

  const MAX_LEN = 200;

  // ── Animation delay per character (ms) ─────────────────────────────────────
  const CHAR_DELAY = 28;

  // ── Core Logic ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  function reverseString(str) {
    // Handles Unicode surrogate pairs / emoji correctly
    return [...str].reverse().join('');
  }

  function isPalindrome(str) {
    if (str.length < 2) return false;
    const cleaned = str.toLowerCase().replace(/[^a-z0-9]/g, '');
    return cleaned.length >= 2 && cleaned === [...cleaned].reverse().join('');
  }

  function countWords(str) {
    const trimmed = str.trim();
    if (!trimmed) return 0;
    return trimmed.split(/\s+/).length;
  }

  function countUnique(str) {
    return new Set([...str].filter(c => c !== ' ')).size;
  }

  // ── Render Animated Characters ──────────────────────────────────────────────
  function renderAnimatedChars(text) {
    // Clear previous content
    outputBox.innerHTML = '';

    if (!text) {
      outputBox.appendChild(outputPlaceholder);
      outputBox.classList.remove('has-content');
      return;
    }

    outputBox.classList.add('has-content');

    const chars = [...text]; // spread handles emoji/unicode
    chars.forEach((char, index) => {
      const span = document.createElement('span');
      span.classList.add('char-span');

      if (char === ' ') {
        span.classList.add('space');
        span.textContent = '\u00A0'; // non-breaking space
      } else {
        span.textContent = char;
      }

      // Stagger the animation
      span.style.animationDelay = `${index * CHAR_DELAY}ms`;
      outputBox.appendChild(span);
    });
  }

  // ── Update UI ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  let debounceTimer = null;

  function updateUI() {
    const raw     = userInput.value;
    const len     = [...raw].length; // emoji-safe length
    const reversed = reverseString(raw);
    const hasText  = raw.length > 0;

    // Character counter
    charCountEl.textContent = `${raw.length} / ${MAX_LEN}`;
    charCountEl.className = 'char-count' +
      (raw.length >= MAX_LEN ? ' max' : raw.length >= MAX_LEN * 0.8 ? ' warn' : '');

    // Animated output
    renderAnimatedChars(reversed);

    // Palindrome badge
    if (isPalindrome(raw)) {
      palindromeBadge.classList.add('show');
    } else {
      palindromeBadge.classList.remove('show');
    }

    // Stats
    statChars.textContent  = len;
    statWords.textContent  = countWords(raw);
    statUnique.textContent = countUnique(raw);

    // Buttons
    copyBtn.disabled  = !hasText;
    clearBtn.disabled = !hasText;
  }

  // ── Copy to Clipboard ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  async function copyToClipboard() {
    const reversed = reverseString(userInput.value);
    if (!reversed) return;

    try {
      await navigator.clipboard.writeText(reversed);
      // Success feedback
      copyBtn.classList.add('copied');
      copyIcon.textContent = '✅';
      copyText.textContent = 'Copied!';

      setTimeout(() => {
        copyBtn.classList.remove('copied');
        copyIcon.textContent = '📋';
        copyText.textContent = 'Copy Reversed Text';
      }, 2000);
    } catch {
      // Fallback for older browsers
      const ta = document.createElement('textarea');
      ta.value = reversed;
      ta.style.position = 'fixed';
      ta.style.opacity  = '0';
      document.body.appendChild(ta);
      ta.select();
      document.execCommand('copy');
      document.body.removeChild(ta);

      copyIcon.textContent = '✅';
      copyText.textContent = 'Copied!';
      setTimeout(() => {
        copyIcon.textContent = '📋';
        copyText.textContent = 'Copy Reversed Text';
      }, 2000);
    }
  }

  // ── Clear ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  function clearAll() {
    userInput.value = '';
    userInput.focus();
    updateUI();
  }

  // ── Event Listeners ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  userInput.addEventListener('input', () => {
    clearTimeout(debounceTimer);
    // Instant update feels snappy for short strings
    // tiny debounce prevents jank on rapid paste of very long text
    debounceTimer = setTimeout(updateUI, 30);
  });

  copyBtn.addEventListener('click', copyToClipboard);
  clearBtn.addEventListener('click', clearAll);

  // ── Init ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  updateUI();
  userInput.focus();
</script>
</body>
</html>
```

## What's included and how it works

### Core Features
- **Real-time reversal** — the output updates as you type with a 30 ms debounce to keep things smooth
- **Character animation** — each character in the reversed output fades and slides in with a staggered delay (`nth-child` colour cycling gives each one a unique colour)
- **Emoji / Unicode safe** — uses the spread operator `[...str]` instead of `.split('')` so emoji and multi-byte characters reverse correctly

### Extra Touches
| Feature | Detail |
|---|---|
| **Palindrome detector** | A gold badge appears when the input is a palindrome (e.g. *racecar*, *A man a plan a canal Panama*) |
| **Live stats** | Shows character count, word count and unique character count |
| **Character counter** | Turns amber at 80 % capacity and red when full |
| **Copy button** | Uses the modern Clipboard API with an `execCommand` fallback; turns green on success |
| **Clear button** | Resets everything and returns focus to the input |
| **Glassmorphism card** | Frosted-glass effect with a deep purple gradient background |
| **Floating icon** | Subtle CSS keyframe animation on the header icon |

